data.description: STUNNING SPLIT-FOYER WITH TWO LIVING AREAS IN THE MEADOWS! Situated on an OVERSIZED LOT in established neighborhood in SONORAVILLE SCHOOL DISTRICT, this gracious, meticulously maintained home features TWO LIVING SPACES and endless possibilities. Guests enter defined greeting foyer, and are welcomed upstairs to the main living level. Gleaming OAK HARDWOODS adorn the spaces of the OPEN-CONCEPT FOOTPRINT. NEWLY RENOVATED KITCHEN with GRANITE COUNTERS met by crisp, shaker cabinetry and STAINLESS APPLIANCE PACKAGE flawlessly flows into the generous living room with SOARING CEILINGS, which opens to the UPPER LEVEL DECKING overlooking the spacious backyard. This is the perfect space for Autumn grilling and get-togethers! Enjoy everyday dining in the kitchenas EAT-IN BREAKFAST NOOK, or more ceremonial dinners in the FORMAL DINING ROOM, complete with decorative ARCHED WINDOW and VAULTED CEILINGS. The owneras retreat is a soothing oasis to begin and end the day. Generously-sized bedroom with TRAY CEILINGS and WALK-IN CLOSET opens to dreamy ENSUITE, complete with: STAND-ALONE TUB featuring FREE-STANDING FAUCET; GEOMETRIC TILE SHOWER with FRAMELESS GLASS enclosure, RAIN HEAD, and BODY SPRAY; and DOUBLE VANITIES. The secondary bedrooms share a generous hall bath with tub/shower combo, accented with dapper tile surround. The homeas LOWER LEVEL is IMPRESSIVE, to say the least! KITCHENETTE (which could be transformed into a full kitchen with minimal effort, and is already wired for future stove/oven) leads to SECOND LIVING ROOM; Large BEDROOM with 2 CLOSETS; HALF BATH (which could be converted to a full bath in the future, if desired); and the MASSIVE LAUNDRY ROOM, which opens to the 2-CAR GARAGE and also to the LOWER LEVEL DECKING. This MOVE-RIGHT-ON-IN-READY home has been tastefully renovated and upgraded to perfection. Make your summers a SPLASH with ABOVE-GROUND POOL, while entertaining family and friends! Enjoy the LUSH, EMERALD LAWN with ESTABLISHED LANDSCAPE, including roses, hibiscus, hostas, Crepe Myrtles, and more! Easily accessed location, convenient to I-75, schools, shopping, dining, and recreation with NO HOA FEES! Welcome Home to 122 Peach Blossom Lane!
